name: Mobquet A-1 Deluxe Floater
Lore: 'Enclosed landspeeder often used by nefarious characters due to its luxury and evasive capabilities. Features include automated steering and fine Corellian leather.',
Text: 'May add 1 driver and 1 passenger. Moves free if Jabba or any bounty hunter aboard. May move for free as a ''react'' to a battle where your thief, smuggler or bounty hunter is participating.',
